00:41:45,627 --> 00:41:46,628
Selesai dipesan.

500
00:41:50,382 --> 00:41:52,842
Perawat Moon tak terlihat sejak kemarin.

501
00:41:53,426 --> 00:41:55,095
Dia sedang ambil cuti.

502
00:41:55,178 --> 00:41:56,012
Apa?

503
00:41:56,471 --> 00:41:57,305
Tiba-tiba?

504
00:41:58,181 --> 00:42:00,266
- Begitu?
- Memangnya kenapa?

505
00:42:02,769 --> 00:42:07,107
Aku ingin berterima kasih kepadanya
untuk kejadian beberapa hari lalu.

506
00:42:08,191 --> 00:42:10,235
Aku berniat mentraktirnya makanan enak.

507
00:42:10,819 --> 00:42:12,487
Traktirlah saat dia kembali.

508
00:42:16,866 --> 00:42:19,869
Tidak ada telepon untukku, 'kan?

509
00:42:20,870 --> 00:42:22,038
Telepon dari…

510
00:42:23,999 --> 00:42:24,833
ayahmu?

511
00:42:25,583 --> 00:42:26,418
Ya.

512
00:42:27,752 --> 00:42:29,879
Jika ayahmu menelepon,
kami harus bagaimana?

513
00:42:33,758 --> 00:42:34,592
Tolong…

514
00:42:35,969 --> 00:42:37,304
beri tahu aku.

515
00:42:37,387 --> 00:42:39,097
- Aku akan memberitahumu.
- Terima kasih.

516
00:42:40,390 --> 00:42:41,224
Selamat bekerja.

517
00:42:43,351 --> 00:42:44,185
Astaga.

518
00:42:46,229 --> 00:42:48,857
Mungkinkah dia ingin mendonorkan hatinya?

519
00:42:50,025 --> 00:42:51,151
Aku tak tahu.

520
00:42:51,860 --> 00:42:56,364
Kenapa Perawat Moon
tiba-tiba mengambil cuti?

521
00:43:09,085 --> 00:43:10,086
Ko Mun-yeong.

522
00:43:12,964 --> 00:43:14,132
Tolong buka pintunya.

523
00:43:40,909 --> 00:43:42,410
Banyak kejadian aneh

524
00:43:44,537 --> 00:43:46,164
yang terjadi di sekitar ayahmu.

525
00:43:46,664 --> 00:43:48,083
Karena itulah aku tahu

526
00:43:50,126 --> 00:43:51,336
bahwa ibumu

527
00:43:52,587 --> 00:43:53,588
masih hidup.

528
00:43:55,882 --> 00:43:56,966
Bu Ok-ran.

529
00:43:59,010 --> 00:44:00,345
Apa pasien itu ibuku?

530
00:44:01,930 --> 00:44:03,139
Karena itukah

531
00:44:04,224 --> 00:44:06,017
kau menghampiriku malam itu?

532
00:44:07,060 --> 00:44:07,894
Bukan.

533
00:44:11,564 --> 00:44:12,440
Kepala perawat

534
00:44:14,776 --> 00:44:16,069
di rumah sakit kami.

535
00:44:17,195 --> 00:44:18,029
Apa?

536
00:44:19,781 --> 00:44:20,949
Park Haeng-ja.

537
00:44:23,284 --> 00:44:24,119
Dia menghilang

538
00:44:26,663 --> 00:44:28,331
setelah menggambar kupu-kupu

539
00:44:29,582 --> 00:44:30,917
di mural Sang-tae.

540
00:44:31,876 --> 00:44:32,877
Tak mungkin.

541
00:44:34,129 --> 00:44:35,463
Dia ibuku?

542
00:44:36,464 --> 00:44:38,091
Meskipun sudah 20 tahun berlalu,

543
