758
01:00:27,022 --> 01:00:30,400
<i>TANGAN DAN SANG MONKFISH</i>

759
01:00:40,577 --> 01:00:42,495
<i>"Dahulu kala,</i>

760
01:00:43,371 --> 01:00:44,497
<i>bayi yang cantik terlahir</i>

