dengan sempurna, lalu dia berkata,

779
01:01:56,110 --> 01:01:58,112
<i>'Anakku yang kucintai.</i>

780
01:01:59,656 --> 01:02:02,075
<i>Ibu harus beristirahat.</i>

781
01:02:03,743 --> 01:02:04,994
<i>Mulai sekarang</i>

782
01:02:06,079 --> 01:02:08,331
<i>tolong sediakan aku makanan.'</i>

783
01:02:10,667 --> 01:02:12,836
<i>Lalu anak itu berkata,</i>

784
01:02:14,754 --> 01:02:18,508
<i>'Ibu. Aku tak punya tangan.</i>

785
01:02:20,134 --> 01:02:22,303
<i>Tanganku menghilang</i>

786
01:02:23,138 --> 01:02:24,806
<i>karena tak pernah digunakan.'</i>

787
01:02:27,809 --> 01:02:29,644
<i>'Kalau begitu,</i>

788
01:02:31,312 --> 01:02:32,897
<i>tolong gendong aku, anakku.</i>

789
01:02:34,774 --> 01:02:36,359
<i>Kakiku sakit.'</i>

790
01:02:38,069 --> 01:02:40,071
<i>Lalu anak itu berkata,</i>

791
01:02:41,823 --> 01:02:46,703
<i>'Ibu, aku tak punya kaki.</i>

